aka
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a. applied to climbing plants and woody  vines, spec. to climbing Metrosideros spp.]  See rata(-vine).  Also occas. other woody vines. Also attrib.
Origin:Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
